 English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aExistential phenomenology. 0aFeminist theory. 0aPostmodernism. 0aSubjectivity. 4aLiterary Studies. 4aWomens Studies.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Backlist 2000-2013z978311053615740uhttps://doi.org/10.7591/978150173183940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501731839423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501731839/original  a978-3-11-053615-7  Cornell University Press Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles